      "item": {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "9b5b3ae4246a0a84",
        "text": "When I first began teaching I found it exhilarating studying my learners. I loved watching as they learned and took pride in the fact that I was the one who had taught them the various products they demonstrated. As an early career teacher hopefully fumbling along, this was the evidence that I must be doing something right – even more reason to watch closely! "
